name: bubble butt
description:
This LoRA model creates anime and semi-realistic characters with bubble butts. Similar to my "hyperass" LoRA but focused on petite bodies with big butts.

v1 Info:
LoRA modes are now supported natively with the latest A1111, but you can also still use the LoRA extension if you don't want to update yet https://github.com/kohya-ss/sd-webui-additional-networks

The keyword for this model is bubble butt but it behaves best if you include ass along with it. Control the butt size with LoRA model strength and tags.

Tips:

  • Place "big" or "huge" before "bubble butt" to add extra size

  • Front facing shots are not really this model's forte. But you can do it if you don't emphasize the ass too much

modelVersions.name: v1
modelVersions.description:
A1111 now has support for LoRA models!

Training Details:

  • 270 images

  • LR 8e-5

  • batch 2

  • GA 8

  • dim 4

  • text captions

  • base model Av3

  • Av3 VAE

  • 30 epocs

  • flip aug

  • clip skip 2

  • both Unet and Encoder training

  • bucketing at 768
